## 🎨 Styling Highlights

### Color Scheme
- **Primary**: Various shades of blue (#3b82f6 family)
- **Secondary**: Indigo, purple gradients
- **Accent**: Green, orange, yellow untuk states
- **Neutral**: Gray scale untuk text dan borders

### Components
- **Cards**: Elevated dengan hover effects
- **Buttons**: Multiple variants (primary, outline, etc.)
- **Badges**: Difficulty dan category indicators
- **Forms**: Modern input styling dengan focus states
- **Navigation**: Smooth transitions dan active states

### Animations
- **Hover Effects**: Scale, translate, shadow changes
- **Loading States**: Smooth transitions
- **Floating Animation**: Background elements
- **Smooth Scrolling**: Enhanced user experience

## 📱 Responsive Design

- **Mobile First**: Optimized untuk mobile devices
- **Breakpoints**: 
  - Mobile: < 640px
  - Tablet: 640px - 1024px
  - Desktop: > 1024px
- **Flexible Layouts**: Grid dan flexbox untuk adaptability
- **Touch-Friendly**: Button sizes dan spacing untuk touch

## 🔧 Customization

### Menambah Template Baru
Edit file `assets/js/data.js`:
```javascript
mockTemplates.push({
    id: 9,
    name: "Template Baru",
    description: "Deskripsi template",
    // ... properti lainnya
});
```

### Mengubah Warna
Edit CSS variables di `assets/css/styles.css`:
```css
:root {
    --primary-500: #yourcolor;
    --primary-600: #yourdarkercolor;
    // ... other colors
}
```

### Menambah Kategori
Edit array `categories` di `assets/js/data.js`:
```javascript
const categories = ['All', 'New Category', ...];
```

